583
00:20:44,240 --> 00:20:46,020
But there's no need to fear them blindly.

584
00:20:46,020 --> 00:20:47,150
Reasonable matters

585
00:20:47,350 --> 00:20:48,960
must be handled properly.

586
00:20:50,350 --> 00:20:52,160
As for doing business...

587
00:20:53,400 --> 00:20:55,270
When trading in Liangjiang,

588
00:20:56,000 --> 00:20:57,060
I have just one rule

