00:20:57,110 --> 00:20:58,040
for you

590
00:20:58,270 --> 00:20:59,310
that you must win;

591
00:21:00,400 --> 00:21:01,720
losing is not an option.

592
00:21:01,720 --> 00:21:03,510
Set boundaries for them.

593
00:21:04,200 --> 00:21:06,000
Don't let them do as they please.

594
00:21:06,200 --> 00:21:06,780
Li Qin,

595
00:21:06,830 --> 00:21:08,590
since you're an imperial court
candidate intendant,

596
00:21:08,590 --> 00:21:09,550
you should wear your official robes.

597
00:21:09,550 --> 00:21:09,920
Yes.

598
00:21:13,830 --> 00:21:14,790
[Righteous and Diligent]

599
00:21:14,790 --> 00:21:16,190
As for the second matter,

600
00:21:16,550 --> 00:21:18,440
the imperial court has issued an edict

601
00:21:18,440 --> 00:21:20,570
to restore the salt and iron monopoly.

602
00:21:21,200 --> 00:21:23,540
Most of the national tax revenue

603
