00:21:24,960 --> 00:21:28,060
So we need to quickly calculate,

605
00:21:28,200 --> 00:21:29,530
in the Jiangnan region,

606
00:21:30,070 --> 00:21:32,470
whether these salt fields have title deeds

607
00:21:32,680 --> 00:21:34,720
