608
00:21:34,830 --> 00:21:36,760
and how many salt stores there are.

609
00:21:36,880 --> 00:21:38,790
Currently
in the Seven Provinces of Jiangnan,

610
00:21:38,790 --> 00:21:40,590
salt is more expensive than rice.

611
00:21:40,590 --> 00:21:42,520
This is absolutely unacceptable.

612
00:21:43,030 --> 00:21:44,230
Except for these two,

613
00:21:44,440 --> 00:21:46,880
the rest of you go immediately

614
00:21:46,960 --> 00:21:47,680
and form groups

615
00:21:47,680 --> 00:21:49,480
to investigate the situation

616
00:21:49,510 --> 00:21:50,480
in each province and county.

617
00:21:50,480 --> 00:21:52,940
Don't delay the imperial court's business.

618
00:21:53,070 --> 00:21:54,000
Yes.

619
00:21:55,730 --> 00:21:56,240
[Liangjiang Viceroy's Office]

620
00:21:56,240 --> 00:21:57,000
The inn

621
00:21:57,030 --> 00:21:58,160
where you stay now

622
00:21:58,880 --> 00:22:00,160
