660
00:23:20,550 --> 00:23:22,790
all nations
should receive equal treatment.

661
00:23:22,790 --> 00:23:24,920
Currently, regarding commercial matters,

662
00:23:24,920 --> 00:23:26,790
there's no way
to further deepen our relationship.

663
00:23:26,790 --> 00:23:27,920
This would be a loss

664
00:23:28,160 --> 00:23:29,160
for both parties.

665
00:23:31,110 --> 00:23:32,350
What do you mean

666
00:23:32,400 --> 00:23:34,400
by going further, Your Excellency?

667
00:23:34,400 --> 00:23:36,590
What do you mean by going further?

668
00:23:37,440 --> 00:23:40,090
[British Envoy]

669
00:23:40,510 --> 00:23:42,440
In businesses such as silk, textile,

670
00:23:42,440 --> 00:23:43,420
tea,

671
00:23:43,590 --> 00:23:44,720
and medicinal herb,

672
00:23:44,750 --> 00:23:45,640
we are qualified

673
00:23:45,640 --> 00:23:46,720
and should be permitted

674
00:23:46,720 --> 00:23:49,120
