702
00:24:58,720 --> 00:25:00,160
by James Hargreaves

703
00:25:00,270 --> 00:25:01,930
and named after his daughter.

704
00:25:01,960 --> 00:25:02,880
It marks the magnificent beginning

705
00:25:02,880 --> 00:25:04,610
of the Industrial Revolution.

706
00:25:07,920 --> 00:25:09,070
This machine can simultaneously

707
00:25:09,070 --> 00:25:10,440
spin 80 spindles.

708
00:25:10,960 --> 00:25:12,510
After numerous modifications,

709
00:25:12,510 --> 00:25:14,030
it now runs on steam power.

710
00:25:16,310 --> 00:25:17,640
Well, we have this kind of machine

711
00:25:17,640 --> 00:25:19,510
