00:27:53,000 --> 00:27:54,270
in our country.

799
00:27:55,070 --> 00:27:56,920
Even if Jiangnan makes an exception,

800
00:27:56,920 --> 00:27:57,520
in the end,

801
00:27:59,070 --> 00:28:01,130
they'll still return empty-handed.

802
00:28:06,720 --> 00:28:07,920
You go ahead. Come on.

803
00:28:11,590 --> 00:28:12,960
I'm so angry at them,

804
00:28:13,000 --> 00:28:13,980
